       attribute within a <meta> tag placed in the documents head section. The recommended encoding is the popular 8-bit 
	   unicode Transformation Format for which the code is UTF-8 -->
 </head>
 
 
 <body>
  <!-- Content in the browswe goes here so that users can see it-->
  <h1> Hello World! </h1>
 </body>
 
</html>